    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that seems like a pretty harsh take... isn't there also a huge debate about whether the UN is even supposed to prevent all wars, or if its real value is just providing a platform for diplomacy so things don't get even worse? i've heard some people say it's basically impossible for any global body to control sovereign nations.",
